# File Upload Guidelines

## AWS S3 Integration
- Use the AWS SDK for S3 operations
- Generate presigned URLs for secure file access
- Implement proper error handling for uploads
- Set appropriate content types and metadata

## File Types
- Videos: MP4, WebM
- Images: JPEG, PNG, WebP
- Audio: MP3, WAV

## Upload Process
- Validate file size and type on client side
- Use server actions for secure upload handling
- Show progress indicators during upload
- Provide clear success/error feedback

## File Access
- Generate presigned URLs with appropriate expiration
- Implement access control based on user role
- Cache URLs to reduce S3 API calls
- Handle expired URLs gracefully
